{"id":36352,"date":"2021-05-25T18:12:37","date_gmt":"2021-05-25T14:12:37","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=36352"},"modified":"2023-10-13T10:23:58","modified_gmt":"2023-10-13T06:23:58","slug":"nations-weak-ummah","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/25\/nations-weak-ummah\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Trials: Nations gather to dominate weak Ummah"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Thawban reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>Soon the nations will be summoned to you just like one is invited to a feast.<\/strong>\u201d It was said, \u201cWill we be few in that day?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>No, rather you will be many in that day, but you will be scum like such flowing down a torrent. Allah will remove your esteem from the chests of your enemies, and Allah will insert feebleness in your own hearts.<\/strong>\u201d It was said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what is this feebleness?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Love for the worldly life and hatred of death.<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4297<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <i>Hasan <\/i>(fair) according to Al-Arna&#8217;ut<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062b\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u064a\u064f\u0648\u0634\u0650\u0643\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0645\u064f \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062a\u064e\u062f\u064e\u0627\u0639\u064e\u0649 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0643\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0643\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0627 \u062a\u064e\u062